.wrapper_with_padding
	#doc_show
		%h1.title=@doc.title
		%p= simple_format(@doc.content)
		
		.buttons
			= link_to "Edit Doc", edit_doc_path(@doc), class: "button"
			= link_to "Delete It", doc_path(@doc), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure?" }, class: "button"
			/ notice the difference between the edit and delete path. also the data attribute sets the message to confirm the delete action.